snippet.title: Street Fighter V - PlayStation Experience 2016: Akuma Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/street-fighter-v-ps4/

The Master of the Fist, Akuma, joins Street Fighter V as the first 2017 DLC Character! Street Fighter V is now available for purchase online and in-stores everywhere. Experience a new era of fighting games!

http://www.streetfighter.com/
